      "background": "Before his transformation, Goran was a renowned High Elf architect. Now, he applies his engineering discipline to maximize the output of the Bloodforge's dark mines. He is a 'Blueblood,' a sub-strain of vampire that retains a more human-like facade, but he is nonetheless bound to Lady Erliza and the dark work of **Castle Bloodforge**.",
