        },
        {
          "name": "Arcane Shot (Fighter 3)",
          "description": "Goran has **2 uses** of this ability (recharges on a short or long rest). Once per turn when he fires an arrow from a shortbow or longbow as part of the Attack action, he can apply one of his Arcane Shot options. Arcane Shot Save DC = **16** (8 + 5 PB + 3 INT Mod).",
          "source": "Fighter Subclass Feature"
        },
        {
          "name": "Heightened Regeneration (Vampire Power)",
