        },
        {
          "name": "Arcane Shot: Bursting Shot",
          "description": "Once per turn, when the +1 Longbow hits a creature, Goran can use a use of Arcane Shot. The creature hit and all other creatures within 10 feet of it take **2d6 force damage each**."
        },
        {
          "name": "Bloodforged Sleep Arrow (Special)",
          "description": "Can be used instead of a normal arrow. When the +1 Longbow hits a target, the creature must succeed on a **DC 16 Wisdom saving throw** or fall **unconscious** for 1 minute. The effect ends early if the creature takes any damage or someone uses an action to wake them. Goran has **5** of these arrows."
        },
        {
          "name": "Charm (Vampire Power)",
          "description": "As an action, Goran targets one creature he can see within 30 ft. The target must succeed on a **DC 17 Wisdom saving throw** (8 + 5 PB + 4 CHA Mod) or be charmed for **24 hours**. While charmed, the target regards Goran as a trusted friend, and Goran can issue them **Command-like orders**. **The target can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success, if it takes damage from Goran or his allies**."
        },
        {
          "name": "Children of the Night (Vampire Power)",
          "description": "Between dusk and dawn, Goran can summon **8d4 swarms of bats or rats**, or outdoors **12d6 wolves**. They arrive in 2d4 rounds, obey his commands, and remain for 2 hours or until dismissed or Goran is reduced to 0 HP. This power resets on a short rest."
        }
